column4: you've got a lot of trucks going into depots IF - is there a sale on? lol

ah ok - yeah someone expanded a public station which blocked my future interchange

as i have 25 trucks waiting on that line

A, to/from York Car Assembly plant

and check with them before doing anything
where do you want to make a junction ?

he is taking goods from there that would otherwise have gone in Finn's trucks
without that airport the only place for goods is in Finn's trucks

if it doesn't have a choice, it will load Finn's trucks
